text: == Births == * February 25 – George Reid, 4th Prime Minister of Australia (d. 1918) * March 27 – Wilhelm Röntgen, German physician and Nobel Prize Laureate * 10 March - Alexander III of Russia , Czar of Russia and father of Czar Nicholas II . Deaths June 8 - Andrew Jackson, 78, seventh President of the United States, tuberculosis, dropsy and heart failure (b. 1767) == New Books == *Queen Margot by Alexandre Dumas, père
